
Chapter 5: CSS Text Properties

1. text-align property:

the text-align property defines the direction our text in webpage.

6 Values:

1. center - change direction of text to center
2. left - which is bydefault
3. right - change direction of text to right
4. start - change direction of text to left
5. end - change direction of text to right
6. justify - balanced left and right margins

the text align property depends on parent element.
and alignment does not change according to doucment but parent elements. 
our text parent element is the body tag
and our texts are the child tags of body tag

